Package: ai-timer-worked
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv, python3-pip, python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, libnotify-bin, zenity, postgresql, postgresql-contrib, curl, ca-certificates, openssl
Recommends: gir1.2-ayatanaappindicator3-0.1 | gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1
Maintainer: VladimirMenshikov <vl.ai.zc.993587@gmail.com>
Description: ai-timer-worked - system tray work timer + local dashboard
 Tray application for Linux Mint / Cinnamon that logs work sessions
 (start/pause/resume/stop) to a local PostgreSQL database, plus a
 Next.js web dashboard (http://localhost:3000) with weekly/monthly
 reports. The package installer sets up local PostgreSQL, Node.js,
 database migrations and both applications end to end.
